                     <interp inst="t17990109-8-off49" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17990109-8-off49" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t17990109-8-cd50" type="crimeDate">29th of December</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17990109-8-off49 t17990109-8-cd50"></join>, a hempen sack, value 2s. and three pecks of wheat, value 5s.
            </rs> the property of 
               <persName id="t17990109-8-victim127" type="victimName">
                  Peter 
                  Lacey
               <interp inst="t17990109-8-victim127" type="surname" value="Lacey"></interp>
